The ex-king of Spain , Juan Carlos , was leading a double life and having an affair with a German aristocrat for the last ten years of his reign .
The allegation is that Juan Carlos was romancing Corinna zu Sayn-Wittgenstein and was so smitten with her that he even contemplated divorcing his wife , Sofia , according to Final De Partida -- or End Game -- by Ana Romero .
Their affair is said to have ended in 2014 .